    "systemalignment": "USFP",
    "metadata": {
        "sysdescription": "Helios has an infamous history. In 2240 it was the center ofa hegemony superweapon, The Planet was deemed a class 6 Bio Hazard and is uninhabited to this day, the uncounted millions who perished are memorialized in an orbital station, with a large habitation complex holding many of the former citizens. As a boarder system it sees moderate traffic and is a hive of smuggling though has little piracy.",
        "security": "Normal",
        "exports": [
            "Denebite",
            "Mining",
            "Nano-Materials",
            "Medical Supplies"
        ],
        "focus": "Trade & Logistics",
